)@@G@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@A@@@@        CONTR  .  TRIAD DEFINITION  @A@@@@        RGS CL
)@@G@@ .  DEFINE THE REGISTERS@]@@@@$(1)  .     @#@@@@         LIT .    @G@@@@CM
)@@G@@.      THIS SECTION RECOMPUTES THE ARGUMENTS OF THE FLD FUNCTION SO THATCN
)@@G@@@G@@@@.      THEY CAN BE USED DIRECTLY IN PHASE V WITH OUT FURTHER COMPUCO
)@@G@@TATION@A@@@@.      THE FOUR CASES CONSIDERED ARE@ @@@@.      LOAD COUNTICP
)@@G@@NG FROM LEFT@#@@@@.        LSSC   F @^@@@@.        SSL    36-N    @A@@@@CQ
)@@G@@.      LOAD COUNTING FROM RIGHT     @#@@@@.       SSC    F+1@^@@@@.     CR
)@@G@@   SSL    36-N    @A@@@@.      STORE COUNTING FROM LEFT     @ @@@@.     CS
)@@G@@   LSSC   F<N    TT2+1  @ @@@@.        DSL    N      TT2    @ @@@@.     CT
)@@G@@   SSC    F      TT1    @A@@@@.      STORE COUNTING FROM RIGHT    @ @@@@CU
)@@G@@.       SSC    F+1-N     TT2+1@ @@@@.        DSL    N      TT2    @ @@@@CV
)@@G@@.       SSC    35-F    TT1    @E@@@@N3FLD*  SR,H2  R4,POLG    FLAG TO NOCW
)@@G@@T PERMUTE SIGNS IN FLD  @^@@@@          SZ,H2    POLG @H@@@@        SZ  CX
)@@G@@   FLDSEX                                                   FLDSGN@E@@@@CY
)@@G@@        L       A1,F31-2,NSEQN  .  THE SECOND COMMA MUST BE @ @@@@      CZ
)@@G@@  SR,S6   R4,MINTX+056  @G@@@@        AND     A1,(0777700,0777777)  .  TDA
)@@G@@REATED DIFFERENTLY IN THE FLD @G@@@@        TNE     A2,(0102100,07)  .  DB
)@@G@@FUNCTION SO THAT NO CONVERSIONS     @E@@@@        S,T3    R5,F31-2,NSEQNDC
)@@G@@  .  WILL BE DONE ACROSS IT   @G@@@@        JNBL    A14,COPND1,0,S3 4 FLDD
)@@G@@DA      CHECK FOR NEGATIVE SIGN     @I@@@@        JE     A15,COPND1,0,S1DE
)@@G@@ 3 FLDA     A NEGATIVE CONSTANT IS AN ERROR IN P5     @^@@@@        SLJ DF
)@@G@@    UPSL    @ @@@@        MVW     COPND1 COPND2 @F@@@@        MVW     (0DG
)@@G@@70000,0) COPND1      ABS OPERATOR IS INSERTED TO@F@@@@        MVW     (0DH
)@@G@@102000,0102) COPER   ELIMINATE (-0) SHIFT COUNTS@F@@@@        LMJ     B9DI
)@@G@@,TSXFX               NUMBER OF ABS EXPRESSION   @^@@@@        L       A5DJ
)@@G@@,SUBNO@^@@@@        SLJ     LWSL    @ @@@@        S       A5,COPND1     DK
)@@G@@@F@@@@FLDA    JNBL    A14,COPND2,0,S3 4 FLDZ     CHECK FOR MINUS SIGN   DL
)@@G@@@H@@@@        SZ,S3  COPND2       REMOVE MINUS SIGN                     DM
)@@G@@      FLDSGN@H@@@@        S      R4,FLDSEX                              DN
)@@G@@                  FLDSGN@H@@@@        JE      A15,COPND2,0,S1 3 FLDZ   ADO
)@@G@@ NEGATIVE CONSTANT IS AN ERROR IN P5@^@@@@        SLJ     UPSL    @A@@@@DP
)@@G@@        MVW     (070000,0) COPND1   @A@@@@        MVW     (0102000,0102)DQ
)@@G@@ COPER@^@@@@        LMJ     B9,TSXFX@^@@@@        L       A5,SUBNO@^@@@@DR
)@@G@@        SLJ     LWSL    @ @@@@        S       A5,COPND2     @D@@@@FLDZ  DS
)@@G@@  L      A1,FNC    ONLY FLD WHICH IS UNNESTED   @E@@@@        AN,M   A1,DT
)@@G@@1    SHOULD GENERATE CODE AS IF IT  IS    @E@@@@         TNZ,H2    SUBLVDU
)@@G@@    .   ALL TO RIGHT IN SUBSCRIPTS  @C@@@@        TE,H2  A1,F31C    TO LDV
)@@G@@EFT OF EQUALS     @^@@@@        J      FLD1     @D@@@@        L      A0,DW
)@@G@@LSEQ    LOCATION OF EQUALS OPERATION@^@@@@        L,M    A1,8     @ @@@@DX
)@@G@@        TNE,S1  A1,F31+1,A0   @^@@@@        J      FLD1     @D@@@@      DY
)@@G@@  L,S2   A0,STTYA      EXPRESSION IN OUTPUT LIST@F@@@@        TNE,M   A0DZ
)@@G@@,37     APPEAR AS IF THEY ARE TO RIGHT OF EQUALS@^@@@@        J       FLEA
)@@G@@D1    @^@@@@        S,S6   A1,COPER @^@@@@FLDB   TZ,H2    COMFL   @E@@@@EB
)@@G@@        J       FLD2       GENERATE EXPRESSIONS FROM RIGHT  @E@@@@      EC
)@@G@@    TNZ,S3   CRRELN             COMPILER (FLD=ABS)    @^@@@@          J ED
)@@G@@       FLD8J@^@@@@          SLJ      UPSL @ @@@@          L         A5,CEE
)@@G@@OPND1 @E@@@@          SLJ      CHEX               GET ABS OF COPND1     EF
)@@G@@@ @@@@          LX,H2    B1,CTRST   @A@@@@          S        A5,TRST-10,EG
)@@G@@B1    @A@@@@          L        A5,TRST-9,B1     @^@@@@          SLJ     EH
)@@G@@ CHEX @ @@@@          L,H2     B1,CTRST   @A@@@@          S        A5,TREI
)@@G@@ST-9,B1     @^@@@@          SLJ      LWSL @]@@@@FLD8J .     @^@@@@      EJ
)@@G@@  LMJ     B9,TSEX @ @@@@        MVW     SUBNO FLDC1   @^@@@@        SLJ EK
)@@G@@    UPSL    @G@@@@        SLJ     FORMSM     FORM EXPRESSION THAT IS SUMEL
)@@G@@ OF 2 OPERANDS    @ @@@@FLD3    LMJ     B11,CHTS+1    @]@@@@        NOP EM
)@@G@@@F@@@@        SLJ     CHEX     CHECK TO SEE IF RESULT US EXPRESSION     EN
)@@G@@@ @@@@        S       A5,COPND2     @ @@@@        MVW     FLDC1 COPND1  EO
)@@G@@@B@@@@        MVW     (0102100,07777) COPER     @I@@@@        JNE     A1EP
)@@G@@5,COPND2,0,S1  5  $+6                                    CSC17    @ @@@@EQ
)@@G@@        LA      A0,COPND2     @^@@@@        SA      A0,FL30 @I@@@@      ER
)@@G@@  LMJ     B11,ITVSX+1                                                CSCES
)@@G@@17    @ @@@@        LMJ     B11,CHTS+1    @F@@@@        SLJ     XERV    ET
)@@G@@            .  CANT REDUCE TO A COMMA     @^@@@@        SLJ     LWSL    EU
)@@G@@@^@@@@        L       B11,CHTS@B@@@@        SZ,H2   POLG  .  CLEAR SIGN EV
)@@G@@FLAG  @F@@@@        J       1,B11               .  RETURN TO ORIGINAL PREW
)@@G@@OGRAM @^@@@@FLD1    SLJ     UPSL    @I@@@@        SR,S6   R4,MINTX+056  EX
)@@G@@      SET BIT SO FLD CAN NOT BE COMMON EXP   CSC24    @I@@@@        SLJ EY
)@@G@@    CHJ  .  CHECK FOR J FACTORS                                CSC24    EZ
)@@G@@@E@@@@        SR,H2   R4,POLG  .  FLAG NOT TO PERMUTE SIGNS IN FLO@A@@@@FA
)@@G@@        MVW     (030100,36) COPND1  @A@@@@        MVW     (0101200,0) COFB
)@@G@@PER   @ @@@@        L,S3    A14,COPND2    @^@@@@        XOR,M   A14,4   FC
)@@G@@@D@@@@        S,S3    A15,COPND2  .  MULTIPLY BY MINUS 1    @ @@@@      FD
)@@G@@  LMJ     B11,CHTS+1    @]@@@@        NOP @^@@@@        SLJ     CHEX    FE
)@@G@@@^@@@@        LX,H2   B1,CTRST@ @@@@        S      A5,TRST-9,B1   @E@@@@FF
)@@G@@        TNZ,H2   COMFL       TEST FOR FLD COUNTED FROM RIGHT@^@@@@      FG
)@@G@@  J       FLD4    @ @@@@        L       A6,(030100,1) @ @@@@        S   FH
)@@G@@    A6,COPND2     @^@@@@        L      B1,CTRST @G@@@@        MVW     TRFI
)@@G@@ST-10,B1 COPND1  .  LAST COPND1 TO PRESENT COPND1     @^@@@@        SLJ FJ
)@@G@@    FORMSM  @ @@@@        LMJ     B11,CHTS+1    @]@@@@        NOP @^@@@@FK
)@@G@@        L      B1,CTRST @D@@@@        S      A5,TRST-10,B1    F IS REPLAFL
)@@G@@CED WITH F+1@^@@@@          J        FLD4J@A@@@@FLD4      L        A5,TRFM
)@@G@@ST-10,B1    @E@@@@          TZ,S3    CRRELN             COMPILER (FLD=ABFN
)@@G@@S)    @^@@@@          SLJ      CHEX @ @@@@          LX,H2    B1,CTRST   FO
)@@G@@@A@@@@          S        A5,TRST-10,B1    @^@@@@FLD4J     SLJ      LWSL FP
)@@G@@@B@@@@        SZ,H2   POLG  .  CLEAR SIGN FLAG  @H@@@@        L      A1,FQ
)@@G@@FLDSEX                                                FLDSGN@H@@@@      FR
)@@G@@  LSSC   A1,2                                                     FLDSGNFS
)@@G@@@H@@@@        OR,S3  A1,COPER         SET FLAG FOR SIGN EXTENSION ONTO OFT
)@@G@@PERATOFLDSGN@H@@@@        S,S3   A2,COPER                               FU
)@@G@@                  FLDSGN@E@@@@        J       ROTS  .  CONTINUE WITH NORFV
)@@G@@MAL PROCESSING    @F@@@@.    THE NEXT SECTION GENERATES CODE FOR FLD LEFFW
)@@G@@T OF EQUALS WHEN  @D@@@@.       FLD      PARAMETERS ARE DETERMINED FROM FX
)@@G@@RIGHT @^@@@@FLD2    SLJ     UPSL    @B@@@@        MVW     COPND1 FLDC2  FY
)@@G@@ SAVE F     @E@@@@          TNZ,S3   CRRELN             COMPILER (FLD=ABFZ
)@@G@@S)    @^@@@@          J        FLD2J@ @@@@          L        A5,COPND2  GA

)@@G@@         LIT .    @H@@@@.  THIS SUBROUTINE IS ENTERED WHENEVER A COMMA OJI
)@@G@@R COLON IS IN THE CURRENT     @F@@@@.  TRIAD AND THE FUNCTION LEVEL IMPLJJ

)@@G@@NT FUNCTION LEVEL @H@@@@.  FOR EACH STATEMENT FUNCTION A COMMA COUNT IS JL
)@@G@@KEPT IN S2 OF FNX FOR THE     @ @@@@.  CURRENT FUNCTION LEVEL.    @H@@@@JM

)@@G@@OMMA  @H@@@@.  AND COLON THEY ARE STORED IN A TWO WORD LINKED TABLE (XF5JO

)@@G@@ REMOVES AN EXPRESSION FROM A CHAIN                   NKSBX @H@@@@.     AS
)@@G@@ WHEN ITS USES ARE EXHAUSTED                                      NKSBX AT
)@@G@@@H@@@@.     WHEN ENTERED A3 IS POINTING AT THE EXPRESSION AND THE LOWER AU
)@@G@@HALF  NKSBX @H@@@@.    OF WORD 4 HAS A POINTER TO THE HEAD LINK ON THE CAV
